        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "Figure 3 illustrates the five potential strategic plays. Supplier businesses in more commoditized seg- ments can make three potential plays: (a) win on cost and scale, (b) find a differentiated niche, and (c) go beyond the core of automotive supply into new business mod- els. Those starting with businesses that today are driven heavily by differ- entiating performance innovation for which cus- tomers are willing to pay more face a core choice whether to remain tradi- tional suppliers and (d)",
